            , <rs id="t17890114-51-viclabel258" type="occupation">Esq</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890114-51-victim473 t17890114-51-viclabel258"></join>.</p>
               <p>Second Count. For stealing the same goods, laying them to be the property of 
               <persName id="t17890114-51-victim474" type="victimName">
                  Henry William 
                  Hobbes
               <interp inst="t17890114-51-victim474" type="surname" value="Hobbes"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890114-51-victim474" type="given" value="Henry William"></interp>
